{"tid":130791,"cid":20,"subCid":0,"title":"考車肥佬問題","createTime":"2017-02-22T15:27:04.000Z","updateTime":"2017-02-26T14:55:11.000Z","uid":86672,"like":0,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":0,"replies":[{"pid":"363ee66ab750a9ba44c92daaa0d5951f1674c501","tid":130791,"uid":86672,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-02-22T15:27:04.000Z","msg":"考車果到比人take左肽盤控制不當 嚴重 所以肥左路試<br />\n究竟口為之控制不當<img src=\"/assets/faces/big/@.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 當中有咩需要注意/改善"},{"pid":"ece0949bfa40918fe0bf9e8e5d047a12d9f4944c","tid":130791,"uid":54655,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-02-22T15:28:01.000Z","msg":"點解唔問師傅"},{"pid":"e2bb871af3d4260901637ef6ec27e1e46f21f7c7","tid":130791,"uid":57584,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-02-22T15:44:10.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"d035bbb4ab295614325db604a66db8cf597f5e48","tid":130791,"uid":81203,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-02-22T15:50:31.000Z","msg":"我又係呢樣嚴重<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />又加埋轉彎位置不正確<br />\n真係想知點解呢<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"49347596dfe6d6a97792809ddb2285def7a2d60b","tid":130791,"uid":63440,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-02-22T16:08:07.000Z","msg":"雙手離開左軚盤？"},{"pid":"2602818bdcc1843b639269ba30e148d3f0dfb190","tid":130791,"uid":41010,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-02-22T16:13:44.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote>考車果到比人take左肽盤控制不當 嚴重 所以肥左路試<br />\n究竟口為之控制不當<img src=\"/assets/faces/big/@.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 當中有咩需要注意/改善</blockquote><br />\n軚盤控制不當基本上一定會剔，如果剔嚴重可能係交叉手，或者唔係雙手控實軚盤<br />\n最安全應該係捽豬腸<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n當然有其他情況會比人大剔軚盤控制不當，等其他巴打幫手分享下</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n調頭，泊車，扭軚個陣扭到盡個下應該要扭到盡啱啱好或者早少少就停，一下扭盡左會撞到出聲，考官會見到+聽到，多過一次就會剔控制不當嚴重<br />\n至於有巴打話轉彎位置不正確，考官見到你燈位轉彎個陣轉完跟唔返地下條線，就會剔你轉彎位置不正確<br />\n<br />\n早幾年師傅講過我知<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />未必係事實全部"},{"pid":"2b9d37d0c72484afd2cab917641f00bfc0566138","tid":130791,"uid":8602,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-02-22T16:24:56.000Z","msg":"扭反手軚？"},{"pid":"f090d6ddade032b92f34c8eca8e5ad5c41e2dbcf","tid":130791,"uid":57584,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-02-23T03:00:32.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"e6b6aa8f6dc135c905c836e00ccc8aacfde678b5","tid":130791,"uid":83904,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-02-23T04:24:40.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>考車果到比人take左肽盤控制不當 嚴重 所以肥左路試<br />\n究竟口為之控制不當<img src=\"/assets/faces/big/@.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 當中有咩需要注意/改善</blockquote><br />\n通常都係<br />\n交叉手扭軚<br />\n單手控制軚盤"},{"pid":"dd7f969f1702802551c9f709403f90b2d4535cbf","tid":130791,"uid":86672,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-02-23T15:27:50.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote>考車果到比人take左肽盤控制不當 嚴重 所以肥左路試<br />\n究竟口為之控制不當<img src=\"/assets/faces/big/@.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 當中有咩需要注意/改善</blockquote><br />\n通常都係<br />\n交叉手扭軚<br />\n單手控制軚盤</blockquote><br />\n我應該都冇呢兩款情況 仲會唔會有其他可能。。"},{"pid":"8f3c2380e1ae13f4122121a4a50445e6f2237c8f","tid":130791,"uid":86672,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-02-23T15:29:51.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>點解唔問師傅</blockquote><br />\n我沙駕 非智尊 冇指定師傅跟 肥左之後 有個唔識既呀sir好開心講冇事既 就帶我去交錢<img src=\"/assets/faces/big/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/big/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/big/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/big/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"0e9d56c0b8cad44f00d0c43d022da676734dbde9","tid":130791,"uid":81066,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-02-23T16:59:25.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote>點解唔問師傅</blockquote><br />\n我沙駕 非智尊 冇指定師傅跟 肥左之後 有個唔識既呀sir好開心講冇事既 就帶我去交錢<img src=\"/assets/faces/big/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/big/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/big/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/big/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n水9你, 我第一次肥左又係俾佢咁帶左去旁水<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"883b8f4694a1062e4b2d0190bcdbc929aec327af","tid":130791,"uid":81203,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-02-23T23:55:28.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote>考車果到比人take左肽盤控制不當 嚴重 所以肥左路試<br />\n究竟口為之控制不當<img src=\"/assets/faces/big/@.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 當中有咩需要注意/改善</blockquote><br />\n通常都係<br />\n交叉手扭軚<br />\n單手控制軚盤</blockquote><br />\n咁係咪得轉波個陣先可以單手控"},{"pid":"ffe0ebb93ddd20533df11d01679e19a0cc18f5ae","tid":130791,"uid":84116,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-02-24T00:54:23.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote><blockquote>考車果到比人take左肽盤控制不當 嚴重 所以肥左路試<br />\n究竟口為之控制不當<img src=\"/assets/faces/big/@.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 當中有咩需要注意/改善</blockquote><br />\n通常都係<br />\n交叉手扭軚<br />\n單手控制軚盤</blockquote><br />\n我應該都冇呢兩款情況 仲會唔會有其他可能。。</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n停紅綠燈個陣唔係雙手揸軚盤"},{"pid":"364d91026d4bab47329d3158b76746428743f4dc","tid":130791,"uid":70689,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-02-24T01:49:10.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote><blockquote>考車果到比人take左肽盤控制不當 嚴重 所以肥左路試<br />\n究竟口為之控制不當<img src=\"/assets/faces/big/@.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 當中有咩需要注意/改善</blockquote><br />\n通常都係<br />\n交叉手扭軚<br />\n單手控制軚盤</blockquote><br />\n咁係咪得轉波個陣先可以單手控</blockquote><br />\n係<br />\n冇其他野做緊最好全程揸軚<br />\n另外怕出錯就轉灣時唔好轉波"},{"pid":"3f5bb1af9a9309125d253400ccb3ba26502827ca","tid":130791,"uid":87106,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-02-24T03:54:56.000Z","msg":"我三月七先可以排快期，但依家已經排到四月😞 等得黎都五月先考..咁耐無渣 會好淆<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2017/02/24/115453_cbfa8bd3a32736317cdb321e21348dfe.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2017%2F02%2F24%2F115453_cbfa8bd3a32736317cdb321e21348dfe.jpg&h=11c086b1&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"870b76f7197165c84a302c964c147d2ae2d58c50","tid":130791,"uid":13596,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-02-24T04:07:59.000Z","msg":"你轉完彎係咪隻水離左少少馱盤由佢自動回直呀"},{"pid":"26c7a65cb46eb21f77d704cfc611eb9ce890a47c","tid":130791,"uid":13596,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-02-24T04:08:25.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>你轉完彎係咪隻<span style=\"color: red;\"><span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\">手</span></span>離左少少馱盤由佢自動回直呀</blockquote>"},{"pid":"a60a82ee30d905f031a534db45e43135e390fca4","tid":130791,"uid":41619,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-02-24T04:35:24.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote>你轉完彎係咪隻<span style=\"color: red;\"><span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\">手</span></span>離左少少馱盤由佢自動回直呀</blockquote></blockquote><br />\n所以有時我見到有啲人話回軚可以放手等佢自己回直心諗唔好on9啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n萬一佢唔回咁你咪等炒上行人路再另加510囉<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/369.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/369.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/369.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"9dcb322b891c48c135e8d8cc6588231a54e48bcc","tid":130791,"uid":41619,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-02-24T04:45:13.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>我三月七先可以排快期，但依家已經排到四月😞 等得黎都五月先考..咁耐無渣 會好淆<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2017/02/24/115453_cbfa8bd3a32736317cdb321e21348dfe.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2017%2F02%2F24%2F115453_cbfa8bd3a32736317cdb321e21348dfe.jpg&h=11c086b1&s={SIZE}\" /></blockquote><br />\n<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2017/02/24/124428_00f4232f95291e53702fa26b864f60d7.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2017%2F02%2F24%2F124428_00f4232f95291e53702fa26b864f60d7.jpg&h=f126274d&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n吾你老母<img src=\"/assets/faces/no